  "text": "Two groups of 16 animals each were injected i.p. with 8 × 10 6 NCI-H929 cells. Two additional groups of 10 mice each were injected s.c. with 8 × 10 6 U266 cells. One group of mice for each combination was treated with three weekly doses of hrIL-27 (1 μg/mouse/dose) starting from 8 hours after tumor cells injection. The other group of mice from each combination was injected with PBS (controls) according to the same time schedule. Twenty-one days after tumor cell inoculation, mice were sacrificed and tumor mass was measured, as previously described [CITATION_1] .",
